    <h1 class="page-header__title">Viceroys &amp; Governors-General of India</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">1773–1950 — Governors-General of Bengal, Governors-General of India, Viceroys, and post-independence Governors-General — with key acts, reforms and UPSC associations.</p>
